<section class="section-padding bg-gray-50">
  <div class="container max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 lg:px-8">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto mb-16 text-center">
      <p class="text-small font-bold text-accent uppercase tracking-wider mb-4">How It Works</p>
      <h2 class="text-h2 font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6 leading-tight">
        Three Clear Steps From Conversation to Boardroom Impact
      </h2>
      <p class="text-body-large text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
        A straightforward path designed to reduce friction for directors, protect capacity, and deliver measurable value fast.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8 mb-16">
      <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-card p-8 border border-gray-200 h-full flex flex-col hover-lift transition-all duration-300">
        <div class="w-12 h-12 flex items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-accent text-white text-xl font-bold mb-6 shadow-button">1</div>
        <h3 class="text-h4 font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3">Discovery Consultation</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">30-minute call with Craig to understand your organisation, priorities, and board dynamics.</p>
        <ul class="space-y-2 text-sm text-gray-600">
          <li>Clarify objectives and success metrics</li>
          <li>Agree stakeholders and timelines</li>
          <li>Outline immediate risks to tackle</li>
        </ul>
        <p class="text-xs text-gray-500 mt-auto pt-4">Time commitment: 30 minutes • No obligation</p>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-card p-8 border border-gray-200 h-full flex flex-col hover-lift transition-all duration-300">
        <div class="w-12 h-12 flex items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-accent text-white text-xl font-bold mb-6 shadow-button">2</div>
        <h3 class="text-h4 font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3">Focused Assessment</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">Two-week sprint combining interviews, evidence review, and wellbeing diagnostics as required.</p>
        <ul class="space-y-2 text-sm text-gray-600">
          <li>Board readiness &amp; governance walkthrough</li>
          <li>Culture and wellbeing insights mapped to ISO 45003</li>
          <li>Prioritised action roadmap with investment options</li>
        </ul>
        <p class="text-xs text-gray-500 mt-auto pt-4">Time commitment: 2–3 leadership sessions • Typical duration: 10 working days</p>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-card p-8 border border-gray-200 h-full flex flex-col hover-lift transition-all duration-300">
        <div class="w-12 h-12 flex items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-accent text-white text-xl font-bold mb-6 shadow-button">3</div>
        <h3 class="text-h4 font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3">Advisory Activation</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">Engage on the right cadence—board advisory, project consulting, or executive coaching—to deliver outcomes.</p>
        <ul class="space-y-2 text-sm text-gray-600">
          <li>Monthly or quarterly board sessions</li>
          <li>Implementation support with measurable KPIs</li>
          <li>Ongoing reviews and pulse reporting</li>
        </ul>
        <p class="text-xs text-gray-500 mt-auto pt-4">Time commitment: Custom cadence • Typical advisory cycles start at 12 weeks</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="bg-primary text-white rounded-2xl p-8 md:p-10 shadow-card hover-lift transition-all duration-300">
      <div class="md:flex md:items-center md:justify-between gap-8">
        <div class="mb-6 md:mb-0 max-w-2xl">
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-3">Transparent Investment</h3>
          <p class="opacity-90 leading-relaxed">Project engagements start from £5,000, annual retainers from £20,000, and executive coaching from £500 per session. Every proposal includes a clear scope, deliverables, and success measures.</p>
        </div>
        <a href="/services" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-6 py-3 bg-white text-primary font-semibold rounded-full hover:bg-gray-50 transition-all duration-300 shadow-button hover:shadow-button-hover btn-scale">
          Compare Services
          <svg class="w-5 h-5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 5l7 7-7 7" />
          </svg>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
